        </div> 
    
        <div class="ArticleView"> 
            
            <div class="ArticleContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/kd/News-and-latest-publications/Speeches-and-articles/kunnskapsministerens-taler-og-artikler/taler-og-artikler-av-kunnskapsminister-k/2010/Early-educational-support--an-investment-in-the-future-.html?id=611730" title="">
                        Early educational support – an investment in the future 
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Speech/article, 26.07.2010]</p>
                <p>Education policy has played a major role in developing the economy, and will be even more important in the years to come. It is estimated that human capital constitutes 70-80 percent of Norway’s national wealth. The importance of education is increasing as high-skilled and more productive labour replaces low-skilled occupations.</p>
                
                
